import React, {useState} from 'react' import likeBtn0 from '../../img/Inactive_Meteor_Heart_Icon.png' import likeBtn1 from '../../img/Active_Meteor_Heart_Icon.png' const NASAdata = ({ image }) => { const [liked, setLiked] = useState(false); return (

{image.title}

  • Date: {image.date}
  • Description: {image.explanation}
setLiked((isLiked) => !isLiked)} id="like" className= "likeBtn" type="image" name="submit" alt="submit" src={liked ? likeBtn1 : likeBtn0}>
) } export default NASAdata
